T he Department annually provides the  White House with progress reports on  its Climate Adaptation and Resilience  Plan (CARP), developed in 2021. Under this  plan, the Department has three overarching  climate adaptation and resilience goals: 

 (1) protect the health and safety of personnel; 

 (2) adapt Department facilities, operations, and  mission-critical services to be more resilient to  the impacts of climate change; and (3) lead by  example through showcasing climate adaptation  and resilience solutions.

